3. cs.CV - The paper deals with visual appearances of characters in 2.5D fighting games, which involves computer vision techniques. 
4. cs.GR - The paper discusses the design of a gaming environment and the actions involved in 2.5D fighting games, which falls under the category of graphics. 
5. cs.GT - The paper deals with sequential action orders and combo skills in 2.5D fighting games, which involves game theory concepts.
